\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ p(y,\theta)\mid\theta\in\Theta\right\} $
\end_inset

 is
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
\hat{\theta} & = & \argmax_{\theta\in\Theta}\log p(\cd,\hat{\theta})\\
\pause & = & \argmax_{\theta\in\Theta}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\log p(y_{i};\theta).
\end{eqnarray*}

